REQUIREMENTS
============

ROOT > 5.26


COMPILATION
===========

$ make clean
$ make
$ make install


HTML DOCUMENTATION CREATION
===========================

$ make docs

The documentation will be saved in the htmldoc directory.


USAGES
======

1. Add the lib directory to your LD_LIBRARY_PATH variable so
   ROOT can automatically find the OSCAR classes using the ROOT map
2. Load the dynamic library lib/libOSCAR.so in your ROOT macro
3. Add OSCARS's include directory to the includes of your project and
   link against lib/libOSCAR.so

